                 <p class="date">
                  <span class="month">
                  Nov                  </span>
                  <span class="day">
                    22                  </span>
                  <span class="year">
                    2012                  </span>
                  </p>
                  <h2 class="title"><a href="http://www.thebigpond.eu/2012/11/22/a-career-rises-from-the-grave-a-revisit/" rel="bookmark">A career rises from the grave &#8211; a revisit</a></h2>

                  <div class="meta">

      				      <p>Published by <a href="http://www.thebigpond.eu/author/admin/" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a>  under <a href="http://www.thebigpond.eu/category/opinion/europe/" title="View all posts in Europe" rel="category tag">Europe</a>,<a href="http://www.thebigpond.eu/category/opinion/" title="View all posts in Opinion" rel="category tag">Opinion</a>,<a href="http://www.thebigpond.eu/category/topstories/" title="View all posts in Top Stories" rel="category tag">Top Stories</a> </p>

      			      </div>

      			      <div class="entry">

                    <p>In Germany newspapers and news agencies are closing down now at the rate of almost one per week. Today it was the turn of Financial Times Deutschland (FTD), my favourite local business daily. As a subscriber (2002 till the end) I was convinced the FTD was a far better read than the &#8220;mother paper&#8221; Financial Times on the island.  <a href="http://www.thebigpond.eu/2012/11/22/a-career-rises-from-the-grave-a-revisit/#more-5312" class="more-link">[Read on]</a></p>
                  
                    <p class="post-tags">

                      Tags: <a href="http://www.thebigpond.eu/tag/german-media/" rel="tag">German media</a><br/>
                    </p>

            			</div>

                  <p class="comments">

                    <a href="http://www.thebigpond.eu/2012/11/22/a-career-rises-from-the-grave-a-revisit/#comments" title="Comment on A career rises from the grave &#8211; a revisit">3 responses so far</a>
                  </p>

	        </div>
