                  <h2 class="title"><a href="http://www.thebigpond.eu/2012/07/06/notions-about-the-germans-which-are-wrong/" rel="bookmark">Incorrect notions about the Germans</a></h2>

                  <div class="meta">

      				      <p>Published by <a href="http://www.thebigpond.eu/author/admin/" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a>  under <a href="http://www.thebigpond.eu/category/opinion/europe/" title="View all posts in Europe" rel="category tag">Europe</a>,<a href="http://www.thebigpond.eu/category/opinion/" title="View all posts in Opinion" rel="category tag">Opinion</a>,<a href="http://www.thebigpond.eu/category/topstories/" title="View all posts in Top Stories" rel="category tag">Top Stories</a> </p>

      			      </div>

      			      <div class="entry">

                    <p>A few incorrect notions have been making the rounds in the media &#8211; about Germany&#8217;s &#8220;financial strength&#8221; on the one hand, and its &#8220;desire to control everything and everyone in Europe&#8221; on the other.  <a href="http://www.thebigpond.eu/2012/07/06/notions-about-the-germans-which-are-wrong/#more-5217" class="more-link">[Read on]</a></p>
                  
